'''Launch Bay 81''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|hangar bay]] located on a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] located over [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]]. In [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], during the establishment of [[Echo Station/Legends|Echo Station]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]], [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] launched twin [[M-class fighter]]s from Launch Bay 81.

